        <question><text>Two lead balls density d radius R placed in contact. Face prop to?</text><option id="A">R^4</option><option id="B">R^2</option><option id="C">R^3</option><option id="D">R^6</option><answer>A</answer><explanation>M = d V = d R^3. F = G M M / (2R)^2 = R^6 / R^2 = R^4.</explanation></question>
